reviewText: LOVED IT! would buy again. They are the best,best,best,best. I am running out of words! Why must you put 18 words?
The greatest late Singer of all times on a DVD and best yet got it for a great deal from Amazon Willie Neal Johnson He brought me joy. I have been telling folk about Amazon.
This is a great DVD of Wille Neal Johnson & The Gospel Keynotes.  I looking forward in buying other ones as they are released.  Great, DVD
No matter if it from previous tapes, this DVD is timely, inspirational and worth having.
This is a compilation of things Willie Neal Johnson did.  Nothing new, and not even his better stuff. Seems like somebody was just trying to make a buck.
Some performers got out of order for a moment or two, but overall the DVD is good and lively.
Always make me think of my Daddy and Momma. I lost my Daddy, now I'm surprising my Momma with this DVD of a Legend they loved and could sing...amazingly for the Lord!
I love this dvd great quality product
PURCHASED THIS FOR MY HUSBAND.  HAD IT ON VHS SO HAD TO REORDER.  HE LOVES THIS STYLE OF SINGING AND WILLIE NEAL JOHNSON, ONE OF THE BEST.
